  <div data-component="article-content">


            <p>Halo: Campaign Evolved, one of Microsoft's next big triple-A releases, just got a cool-looking cinematic story trailer. And all footage you'll see in it has been captured on a <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/topics/ps5-pro">PS5 Pro</a>, of course.</p>
<p>The trailer takes you through the core experience of Halo: Campaign Evolved. There are plenty of cinematics to look at, some brief peeks at classic Halo gameplay, and even some shots of iconic original Halo environments reworked within the modern engine.</p>

<figure>
<p>
